---
title: Cheesy Stuffed Burgers with Garlic-Cajun Oven Baked Wedges
description: It's a double cheese stuffed burger extravaganza! Cream cheese is mixed with sharp cheddar and hidden inside juicy beef burgers. These beauties are finished off with tomatoes and Dijonaisse then served with garlic-Cajun potato wedges for the very best burger dinner!
